includedAssets.title: Tinker Bell And The Legend Of The Neverbeast
includedAssets.synopsis: After a night in Pixie Hollow that sees the sky go green, a strange animal awakes deep in the dark underground where a comet landed. Mischievous animal fairy Fawn (voiced by Angela Bartys) is quick to befriend this huge and fearsome-looking critter but Tinker Bell (Mae Whitman) and the other fairies aren't so sure about the scary newcomer. However, when the Scout Fairies decide to capture the beast it's time for Fawn and friends to act.
includedAssets.shortSynopsis: There's concern in Pixie Hollow when Tinker Bell's animal-loving friend Fawn befriends a mysterious creature.

includedAssets.title: Tinker Bell And The Pirate Fairy
includedAssets.synopsis: When the rogue fairy Zarina (voiced by Christina Hendricks) steals Pixie Hollow's supply of fairy dust and joins the pirates of Skull Rock, Tinker Bell leads the pursuit to get it back. But the journey is thrown into confusion when Tink and her companions discover that their talents have been switched! And time is running out because Zarina is about to make a deal with the pirate leader - a young rapscallion by the name of James Hook (Tom Hiddleston). Disney's fairy elite have it all to do in their most swashbuckling adventure yet.
